{"tid":1257613,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"notebook mon唔著，死緊","createTime":"2019-06-25T15:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T00:53:50.000Z","uid":22289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"48bb8ed58c567df4c1a91b864b932e242f175855","tid":1257613,"uid":22289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:45:57.000Z","msg":"想問全能連登仔， <br />\n<br />\nnotebook 本來著，我插左hdmi線見佢連唔到個mon之後改左setting去只顯示另一顯示器，<br />\n<br />\n之後部notebook 就個mon睇唔到野<br />\n但另外hdmi插住個mon都係冇野睇 <br />\n<br />\n要硬restart部機 <br />\n入到safe mode ！safe mode 有野睇，notebook mon 有野但hdmi mon一樣唔得，<br />\n但如果正常restart 就兩個mon都全黑分已冇野睇<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yd7sRYa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYd7sRYa.png&h=1714d2d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n試過另一部notebook 同一條線睇到的。"},{"pid":"51a961e137f87247aac51fb99310bbdc20106d07","tid":1257613,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:48:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forums.pcpitstop.com/topic/191946-windows-key-p-%E2%80%A2-easy-display-switcher/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforums.pcpitstop.com%2Ftopic%2F191946-windows-key-p-%25E2%2580%25A2-easy-display-switcher%2F&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=c1efe353\" target=\"_blank\">https://forums.pcpitstop.com/topic/191946-windows-key-p-%E2%80%A2-easy-display-switcher/</a>"},{"pid":"121e353bd2ae0294ab851b9bc52e843270da6e52","tid":1257613,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:50:03.000Z","msg":"最壞情況 壞HDMI頭"},{"pid":"794b9d7759f7793ac55dd1b1451cfa446336b93d","tid":1257613,"uid":22289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"121e353bd2ae0294ab851b9bc52e843270da6e52","tid":1257613,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:50:03.000Z","msg":"最壞情況 壞HDMI頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"我再試試入safe mode, 撳Window P,冇反應，<br />\n入去控制台 